								How We Vet
							</a>
							<a
								role="menuitem"
								href="/about/our-guarantee/"
								class="flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-xl px-2 py-2 text-xs text-slate-400 transition hover:bg-slate-800/70 hover:text-white focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sky-300"
							>
								<svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12.75V12A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 9.75h15A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 21.75 12v.75m-8.69-6.44-2.12-2.12a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.061-.44H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 6v12a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25h15A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 21.75 18V9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25h-5.379a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.06-.44Z" /></svg>
